title: Adobe Photoshop CS3 For Dummies
description:
Adobe Photoshop CS3 For Dummies
Photoshop CS3 is a powerhouse, and here&#039;s the fast and easy way to get up to speed on all the coolest features. This friendly guide helps you get images into Photoshop - and then turn them into dazzling works of art. You&#039;ll see how to work in the right file formats, master the Brushes palette, get creative with filters, convert color to grayscale, and more!

* Adjust brightness, improve color, and fix flaws
* Take advantage of the Raw file format
* Composite images with layers and blending modes
* Automate your tasks with scripts and Actions
* Apply the new Smart Filters to Smart Objects 
* Much Much More! 


Enjoy!
